        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1305617947" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7250903209981283045">One theory is that the book is based on an actual U.S. ambassador to South Vietnam, Ellsworth Bunker, a rich businessman. He never learned the language or left the compound. He&apos;s only given the information that his staff thinks he ought to have. <br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText7250903209981283045" style="display:none">One theory is that the book is based on an actual U.S. ambassador to South Vietnam, Ellsworth Bunker, a rich businessman. He never learned the language or left the compound. He's only given the information that his staff thinks he ought to have. <br /><br /></span>
