              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2116720414341388555">If you&apos;ve ever heard the term &quot;ugly American&quot; used, this is where it originated. And, if you want to understand why many folks from other countries refer to some Americans using that phrase, this book will make it crystal clear why they do. Excellent read!</span>
  <span id="freeText2116720414341388555" style="display:none">If you've ever heard the term "ugly American" used, this is where it originated. And, if you want to understand why many folks from other countries refer to some Americans using that phrase, this book will make it crystal clear why they do. Excellent read!</span>
